[gd_resource type="Resource" script_class="EnemyStats" format=3]

; The Slinger: the first ranged enemy. Lobs rocks from across the room, which
; breaks the "wait at my tier and they walk to me" answer — you close the gap
; or you parry the rock BACK (projectile.gd gives a returned rock double damage
; and a guaranteed stance break, so the greedy answer stays the stylish one).
; Weak up close on purpose: getting in its face is the reward for approaching.

